  - https://docs.flutter.dev/testing/overview
- Financial consumer protection:
  - https://www.fsb.org/2022/12/cos_111104a/
- Risk assessment:
  - https://csrc.nist.gov/pubs/sp/800/30/r1/final
- Brazil regulatory/open finance:
  - https://dadosabertos.bcb.gov.br/
  - https://openfinancebrasil.org.br/atos-normativos/
- Test strategy:
  - https://www.istqb.org/certifications/certified-tester-test-automation-strategy-ct-tas/

## Expected final delivery format

Before finalizing an implementation, provide:

- Scope and acceptance criteria summary
- Architecture and implementation decisions
- Financial math validation notes
- Automated test plan and evidence
